tool_description: Experience true exclusivity with the Most Exclusive API. Only one user at a time gains access to exclusive content, with exclusiveness passing on every 5 minutes. Be the first to request the API when the previous user's exclusiveness expires and claim your exclusive access.
name: Most Exclusive API
title: Most Exclusive API

api_list.name: /steal-exclusiveness/{callerID}
api_list.description: Steal Exclusiveness. Get exclusive right away even if someone else's time of exclusiveness did not expire.

required_parameters.name: callerID
required_parameters.description: Caller ID. Any string identifying the requester. Be creative. Alphanumeric [a-zA-Z0-9_-] max 32 chars.

api_list.description: Check Exclusiveness. See if you are already exclusive, not yet or you get the exclusivity now.
